Module org.example.proyecto
Package org.example.proyecto.model.booking

Class BookingDTO

java.lang.Object
org.example.proyecto.model.booking.BookingDTO
public class BookingDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for booking information. This class encapsulates the data of a booking and provides methods for accessing and manipulating this data.
Since:
2024-05-28
